                <b><i><a href="http://farsite.hill.af.mil/reghtml/Regs/far2afmcfars/fardfars/Dfars/Dfars252_246.htm#TopOfPage" rel="nofollow me noopener noreferrer" target=_blank">252.246-7007</a>, Contractor Counterfeit Electronic Part Detection and Avoidance System (Aug 2016)</i></b><br> Supplier is currently compliant with DFARS 252.246-7007 or will be compliant if subsequently awarded a purchase order or contract with USG end use.
            </p>
            <ul class="ml75 hr">
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox57252_124262 /> Yes(AB) </b></li>
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox57252_124263 /> No(AA) </b></li>
                <br />
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox57252_124264 /> N/A - Supplier is original manufacturer(AC)</b></li>
                <br />
                <li>
                    <b>
                        <input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox57252_124265 />
                        N/A - Supplier does not provide electronic parts end items, components or assemblies containing electronic parts(AD)
                    </b>
                </li>
                <br />
                <li>
                    <b>
                        <input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox57252_124266 />
                        N/A - Supplier does not provide services where it will provide electronic parts or components, or parts or assemblies containing electronic parts as part of the service(AE)
                    </b>
