                <br />
                <li><b>If <i>No</i>, further comment/explanation required:(AA)</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; @(ViewBag.Checkbox57252_Comment ?? String.Empty)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>


        <div>
            <p class="ml25">
                <b><i><a href="http://farsite.hill.af.mil/reghtml/Regs/far2afmcfars/fardfars/Dfars/Dfars252_246.htm#TopOfPage" rel="nofollow me noopener noreferrer" target=_blank">252.246-7008</a>, Sources of Electronic Parts (Dec 2017)</i></b><br> If you purchase electronic parts from a <u>non</u>-authorized source, do you perform inspection, testing and authentication in accordance with established counterfeit prevention industry standards and processes?
            </p>
