            </ul>
        </div>


        <div>
            <p class="ml25">
                <b><i><a href="http://farsite.hill.af.mil/reghtml/Regs/far2afmcfars/fardfars/Dfars/Dfars252_246.htm#TopOfPage" rel="nofollow me noopener noreferrer" target=_blank">252.247-7022</a>, Representation of Extent of Transportation by Sea (Aug 1992)</i></b><br> Supplier represents it
            </p>
