                <b><i> Are You Ready to Submit Your Complete Certifications and Assessment for Celestica Review and Approval</i></b><br> Once this submission is made you will not be able to change your online Supplier Certifications and Assessment.
            </p>
            <ul class="ml75 hr">
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox57264_Yes /> Yes </b></li>
                <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox57264_No /> No </b></li>
            </ul>
