        @*<p style="text-align:center; font-size:21px"><i><u><b>Overall Certification</b></u></i></p>

            <p>Supplier hereby certifies the information presented here is true and correct and meets the intent and spirit of the statements made above.  This Certifications and Assessment shall apply to all solicitations, agreements, Purchase Orders, contracts, or subcontracts received from Celestica-Aerospace, and shall be valid for the current calendar year.  If any changes to the above occur, supplier will immediately notify their Celestica-Aerospace Sourcing or Procurement representative, in writing, regarding its change in status.</p>
            <p>
                <ul class="ml75 hr">
                    <li><b><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox49582_Yes /> Yes </b></li>
